data.clean_description: Price per 1 gram. Fully purged super strong OG Kush Shatter. Professional extraction , with pronounced hashy and fruity terpenes. A deep transparent amber , This one is proper couch lock Indica , well balanced stone , only a small amount is needed for those with low shatter tolerance. Not advised as a wake and bake dab if you got work to do. Over doing it will leave you incapable of moving lost in a semi psychedelic trance state. This one seems a bit more balanced and not as manic as the Hindu Kush shatter when you have one dab to much. You wo nt be disappointed with this. one at this price.
data.name: OG Kush Shatter 1 Gram
